   <body>
      <p>
         <uicontrol>Audit Trail</uicontrol> is a separate document that Adobe provides when
         generating the final signed document. Once the agreement is signed, a signed copy of the
         PDF is stored within our application. <uicontrol>Power Connector </uicontrol>grabs the last
         generated document from Adobe. If the custom setting for the <uicontrol>audit
            trail</uicontrol> is enabled, then either the audit trail document will be generated
         last, or the final signed document will be generated last. In either case, only the last
         document is grabbed. </p>
      <p>To add the <uicontrol>audit trail document</uicontrol>, you must</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Disable <uicontrol>Audit Trail </uicontrol>setting</li>
         <li>Set up <uicontrol>File Mapping</uicontrol> for <uicontrol>audit trail </uicontrol>
         </li>
         <li>Send for Signature</li>
      </ol>
